import { Meta } from '@storybook/addon-docs/blocks'

<Meta title="storybook-addon-tag-badges/internalBadge" />

# Internal badge

Use the **internal** badge to hide stories from the sidebar during production build. The badge displays 🔒 with an "Internal" tooltip. Internal stories are excluded from the sidebar by default in filter selection.

## Usage

Add the `internal` tag to your story. Configure your `.storybook/main.ts` so that stories with the `internal` tag are excluded from the sidebar in production:

```tsx
export const YourStory = {
	tags: ['internal'],
	render: () => <YourComponent />
}
```

In `.storybook/main.ts`:

```ts
export default {
	tags: {
		internal: {
			excludeFromSidebar: process.env.NODE_ENV === 'production'
		}
	}
}
```

Build with:

```sh
NODE_ENV=production storybook build
```

